{"tid":751912,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"Flipper's 食評","createTime":"2018-07-22T10:08:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-22T15:46:18.000Z","uid":175988,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f191f8ddc33a2659dcc0c7c19e4fd7936373d818","tid":751912,"uid":175988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T10:08:51.000Z","msg":"<strong>Flipper's @ CWB</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/YzgnVVn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FYzgnVVn.jpg&h=bdba8534&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>原味班戟</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n外層煙韌，內裡軟綿有空氣感，整體質感幾好<br />\n<br />\n蛋香甚濃，唔講仲以為食緊厚燒玉子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n忌廉輕盈，butterscotch香味出，又唔會過甜過膩<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n糖霜完全畫蛇添足，cream同pancake本身已經有足夠甜味，亦唔覺加完碟嘢靚咗幾多<br />\n<br />\nCream打得唔夠滑，影響口感<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>結論: 蛋味濃呢點已經無得輸，值得一試<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong>"},{"pid":"583736308681d64395b6f86cf28d2e007ac80918","tid":751912,"uid":158537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T10:15:30.000Z","msg":"係幾好食。不過希慎店排隊算係耐，入口即溶，排得耐坐唔得耐。性價比低，唔係帶女去試未必會去。"},{"pid":"d47237b458ac43e1167b13f355a0127e877e327c","tid":751912,"uid":175988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T11:11:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e3d9bc02753b190b5768304711f8b3fa2d6dd60","tid":751912,"uid":7878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"583736308681d64395b6f86cf28d2e007ac80918","tid":751912,"uid":158537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T10:15:30.000Z","msg":"係幾好食。不過希慎店排隊算係耐，入口即溶，排得耐坐唔得耐。性價比低，唔係帶女去試未必會去。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T11:40:49.000Z","msg":"唔係帶女都唔會去食pancake啦<img src=\"/a